'''Rikknit eggs''' were the primary export of [[New Plympto/Legends|New Plympto]], homeworld to the [[Nosaurian/Legends|Nosaurians]]. When New Plympto joined the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], they were denied representation, but the [[Egg/Legends|eggs]] were continually used as a source of the delicacy. Soon enough, however, the demand for [[Rikknit/Legends|rikknit]] eggs dried up after the Republic declared the rikknit's a protected [[Species/Legends|species]], and New Plympto was deprived of its only export. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], New Plympto joined the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] movement with the promise of reviving the market for rikknit eggs.

Preserved rikknit eggs had a pungent smell.

